( Carnage: Yes, Dinobot meant Mosquitor but I was not sure if it was him. I 
deleted the message before I could grasp the name. And I was mistaken, it 
was acid. Sorry. But the affects are still the same.)

* Dinobot snarled at Mosquitor's cry of rage, as far as he was concerned 
nobot could just expect to harm another and expect him to just stand and 
watch! Even if it meant being pelted with acid!
He looked the Predacon straight in the optic and bared his teeth...*

" As long as I am functional I will strive to rid the universe of scum like 
you!"

* Even though the drops of acid upon his chest sent waves of pain through 
his body he stood tall and proud, and he would continue to do so either 
until this war had ended or his spark had ceased to exist.
It was then that the second wave of acid hit him, Dinobot snarled as the 
pain intensified but still stood his ground, thankful that it wasn't 
Tavatron who felt this excruciating pain!
Dinobot wiped the acid from his chest-plate but where it had hit his armor 
was weakening, he knew that if anything he had to protect Tavatron from this 
stuff and try and keep his spark from being hit at the same time.
Not an easy task!
Dinobot snarled and roared as he targeted and shot at Mosquitor with both 
his optic laser and the rifle, he would not give up...no matter the cost!*
